drm/panel: Add Sharp LS043T1LE01 MIPI DSI panel

The Sharp LS043T1LE01 is a 4.3", 540x960 TFT-LCD panel connected using
two DSI lanes. It is for example found on the Qualcomm Snapdragon 800
Dragonboard (APQ8074).

